Package com.cs546.backend.core.components

  • Class Summary
    Class Description
    Component
    This is the base component that all other components in the city must extend.
    EmptyComponent
    Empty component that does not do anything
    IndustrialComponent
    Industrial component that represents a factory.
    PowerComponent
    Generates power for components in the city.
    RailComponent
    Rail component that can be used to build up rail connections.
    ResidentialComponent
    This represents a house component that is needed for people to live in the city.
    RetailComponent
    This represents a shop and is needed for the city to make profit.
    RoadComponent
    Represents a road in the city.
  • Enum Summary

    Possible types a component can have.
    PowerType
    Possible types a power component can have.
